Lovers of the popular reality television show, Big Brother Naija are in for a fun time as the BBNaija Lockdown Reunion Show premieres today. The show which will be hosted by Ebuka Obi-Uchendu will revisit some highlights and memorable moments from the 2020 season 5 edition that saw Laycon emerge as the winner. BBNaija fans from across the world will see their favourite lockdown housemates set the record straight about any issue they had with each other on the Reunion Show. More so, the reunion show will enable fans to relieve some of the passionate moments on the Lockdown edition, as well as heated moments. The reunion show will leave fans of the reality TV show nostalgic.